 Development Manual
====================

 Gems Management
=================

http://gembundler.com

   gem install bundler

   bundle install        # update Gemfile.lock against Gemfile changes
   bundle update [<gem>] # update Gemfile & Gemfile.lock for gem/s upgrade
                         # ... needed if install fail due to unresolved dependencies
   git add Gemfile Gemfile.lock # add changes to git
   # git commit -m 'gem dependencies updated'

 Program & Tests  Execution
============================

   bundle exec [app params...]           # execute bundled app
   bundle exec rspec spec/flickru_spec:N # execute rspec line N

 Gem Release
=============

http://github.com/svenfuchs/gem-release

   mv flickru /tmp # flickru is generated by bundle
                   # unfortunately, bump tries to bump versions inside it too
   gem bump --version (major|minor|patch) # this commit all the stagged changes,
                                          # which should be only the ones derived
                                          # from bumping the gem version
   mv /tmp/flickru .

rake release # release, push to GitHub and rubygems
